import React from 'react'
import {FaBars} from 'react-icons/fa'
import { 
        Nav, 
        NavbarContainer,
        MobileIcon,
        NavMenu,
        NavItem,
        NavLinks    
    } from './navbarElements';

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Nav>
          <NavbarContainer>
            <MobileIcon>
              <FaBars />
            </MobileIcon>
            <NavMenu>
              <NavItem>
                <NavLinks to="about">
                  
                </NavLinks>
              </NavItem>
            </NavMenu>
          </NavbarContainer>
        </Nav>
      </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
